In previous lectures, you were introduced to DQN - an algorithm that falls under the first major branch of Reinforcement Learning, &ldquo;Value Based Methods&rdquo;. In this lecture, we introduce you to &ldquo;Policy Gradient methods&rdquo; the second major branch of Reinforcement Learning where we learn to manipulate the object we care about the most - the policy - directly.

